task.summary: Created a banking application on Spring Framework support that accepts two type of money transfer between accounts: intra-bank and inter-bank. It is organised in three modules: Data, that persist the data in the PostgreSQL database with the help of Hibernate, Business, that implements the logic of the application and Controller, which takes a request and maps it to the specific URI to return the expected response. It also contains integration test and unit tests to verify the functionality of the program.
